  <li>â€œWhy do atoms stick together to form molecules?â€</li>
  <li>â€œHow do we determine and understand structures of biomolecules?â€</li>
</ul>

<p>The course requires one year each of general chemistry and organic chemistry (CHEM 101, 202, 211, 212) as well as MATH 217 and 231. BIOL 301 is recommended.</p>
